    "shortName": {
      "zh": "凯门鳄",
      "en": "Caiman"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "凯门鳄复合防弹头盔是新一代轻量级特种部队装备的代表之一。尽管原版头盔只有防撞作用，但不知道怎么的在塔科夫突然就能防弹了——就当是诺文斯克特有的魔法吧。由 Galvion 公司设计制造，复合迷彩版本。",
      "en": "The Caiman Hybrid helmet is a new generation of lightweight special forces helmet. This bump version, through some Tarkov magic, features a protection level similar to normal ballistic helmets. Manufactured by Galvion. MultiCam camouflage version."
    },
